Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.51,0:00:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新機動戰記-鋼彈W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.71,0:00:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.18,0:00:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.72,0:00:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.83,0:00:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著你被淋濕的肩膀 想溫暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.04,0:00:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顫抖的指尖 徬徨地在找甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.84,0:00:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.12,0:01:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲傷變為力量的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.56,0:01:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.23,0:01:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.87,0:01:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.57,0:01:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.52,0:01:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.55,0:01:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這是鄉間小路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.49,0:01:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.89,0:01:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個美麗的大自然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.49,0:01:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令我的心十分滿足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.73,0:01:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，我已經不是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.67,0:01:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不用那麼關心我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.77,0:01:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.14,0:01:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是羅姆斐拉財團所有的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.71,0:01:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉財團\N從前想以他的財力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.28,0:01:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保護這個美麗的大自然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.41,0:02:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我才贊同他的精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.18,0:02:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在地球圈統一聯合內部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.02,0:02:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,創立SMS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.29,0:02:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\N那些擁有反叛翅膀的他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.79,0:02:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擋在我們面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.43,0:02:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十八話\N[交錯的命運]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.62,0:02:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星派來的\N鋼彈合金製機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.09,0:02:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.62,0:02:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那班優秀的駕駛員們前來挑戰我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.97,0:03:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫五飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.58,0:03:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯‧克修里那達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.06,0:03:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.83,0:03:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.44,0:03:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種力量和勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.71,0:03:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們的每一次行動\N令我的心著迷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.44,0:03:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令我不得不振奮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.15,0:03:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那方面你也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.58,0:03:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯‧馬吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.12,0:03:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.75,0:03:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也應該為了目的單純地戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.03,0:03:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把山克王國\N從聯合手上解救出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.00,0:04:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機動戰士，全體出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.17,0:04:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，我也出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.01,0:04:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請交由我掩護
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.74,0:04:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你只想著達到目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.41,0:04:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已心無雜念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.55,0:04:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新型機動戰士正急速接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.99,0:04:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有光線砲集中攻擊那部機體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.82,0:04:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我用了13年時間\N才再次踏上這片土地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.79,0:04:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你原諒我，父王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.69,0:05:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，很多人因此流盡鮮血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.20,0:05:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只能過著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.40,0:05:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,違背你完全和平主義的生活方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.40,0:05:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的手被血染得太污穢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.44,0:05:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣的我不能繼承\N匹斯克拉福特王族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.68,0:05:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，她應該一定能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.25,0:05:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,建立爸爸你理想中的國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.41,0:05:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會為了那目標而戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.85,0:05:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請原諒我這個不肖子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.66,0:05:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們站在歷史的表面舞台上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.49,0:05:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令時代向正確的方向前進了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.43,0:05:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的地方是宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.96,0:05:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安\N我把宇宙交給妳處理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.77,0:05:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向衛星的人宣揚我們的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.67,0:05:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果以友愛的態度和他們接觸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.14,0:05:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們也就會了解我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.31,0:05:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.32,0:05:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球圈統一聯合崩潰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.65,0:06:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\N宇宙有聯合的殘餘勢力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.72,0:06:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討伐他們，解放衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.86,0:06:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓衛星獨立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.83,0:06:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是奉命處理宇宙的我的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.17,0:06:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對，這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.03,0:06:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯大人和我們的OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.40,0:06:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該反省
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.40,0:06:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和迪爾麥優侯爵的意見對立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.84,0:06:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而鋼彈的駕駛員們就成為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.88,0:06:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個不斷轉變的歷史的見証人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.95,0:06:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安特校!地球有通訊來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.42,0:06:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新加坡宇宙港基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.75,0:06:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正受到鋼彈02和04的攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.39,0:06:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上回去司令部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.43,0:06:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點!卡特爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.77,0:06:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別管我\N我決定了要掩護你們升空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.87,0:06:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋!你說甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.87,0:06:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家一定要去宇宙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.51,0:06:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，所以我在這裡掩護大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.95,0:06:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少你們兩個能去到宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.28,0:07:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.22,0:07:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.05,0:07:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下…剩下的武器…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.66,0:07:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有自爆裝置呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.37,0:07:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.57,0:07:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…想叫我下去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.07,0:07:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沙漠鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.42,0:07:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝你，你的沙漠鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.23,0:07:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，他們前往的宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.17,0:07:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有慰問和讚賞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.31,0:08:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有被當作叛亂份子的象徵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.48,0:08:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孤立和殘酷的命運在等待他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.77,0:08:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的行動會受到很大的限制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.94,0:08:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,束縛會成為戰敗者...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.64,0:08:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一次力量的基礎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.58,0:08:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\N現在的我反而覺得自由了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.68,0:08:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許一直以來不大自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.85,0:08:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我採取的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.25,0:08:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為自己帶來好的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.89,0:08:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.16,0:08:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你克服了我給你的考驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.60,0:08:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贏得自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.10,0:09:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯!別那麼執著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.52,0:09:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯，我不能成為你的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.26,0:09:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,永別了，特列斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.57,0:09:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你離去後，羅姆斐拉財團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.07,0:09:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以茲巴洛夫技師長為中心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.27,0:09:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把感覺不到\N戰鬥的美麗和悲傷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.94,0:09:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.81,0:09:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們想用它們從宇宙支配地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.88,0:09:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尋求人與人的戰鬥意義的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.35,0:09:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能同意他們這種想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.96,0:09:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.69,0:09:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有你的OZ會容許
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.29,0:10:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒用的人做出無益的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.51,0:10:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯‧克修里那達\N你果然厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.01,0:10:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙正逐漸認同OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.58,0:10:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.01,0:10:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安特校的表現好出色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.68,0:10:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她陸續和衛星建立起友好關系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.99,0:10:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在宇宙建立國家的獨立心態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.82,0:10:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會生產出防衛意識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.99,0:10:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後以軍事國家的身份站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.06,0:10:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球的各國感到威脅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.46,0:10:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就會爭先恐後尋求OZ的支配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.53,0:10:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了不起，特列斯，想不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.84,0:10:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你把宇宙變為羅姆斐拉的一份子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.47,0:10:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星是虛假的生活空間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.81,0:10:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虛假的和平主義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.21,0:10:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許只是\N產生更激烈戰爭的溫床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.78,0:10:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯，不，米利亞爾特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.48,0:10:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你發覺到那一點嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.03,0:11:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於宇宙衛星和OZ合併
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.69,0:11:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙的形勢對地球影響很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.90,0:11:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我以一個國家的代表身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.53,0:11:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前來這裡打聽那方面的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.24,0:11:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個國家?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.60,0:11:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我忘了自我介紹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.97,0:11:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是山克王國的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.91,0:11:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米利亞爾特‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.44,0:11:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你從大人自小就有交情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.98,0:11:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王國前來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.78,0:11:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽聞她在今次戰亂中\N開始復興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.75,0:11:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想知道戰爭會帶來甚麼的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.62,0:11:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能向想擁有武力的衛星好的建言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.03,0:11:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尋求和平有很多方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.26,0:11:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起學習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.70,0:11:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朝著更好的方向前進吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.30,0:11:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳或許正在走一條明智的路呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.24,0:11:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.61,0:11:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心愛的蕾蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.51,0:11:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是正確的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.52,0:12:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個世上只要有人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.56,0:12:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰爭就絕對不會消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.56,0:12:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而否定戰爭不是步向和平之路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.07,0:12:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界繼續戰鬥是自然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.38,0:12:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.35,0:12:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯和鋼彈的駕駛員們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.62,0:12:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在正創造未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.69,0:12:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥的人有充實的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.43,0:12:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而戰鬥的人不會墮落也是事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.60,0:12:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.20,0:12:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是任何東西也難以替代的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.57,0:12:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為豁出一切挑戰敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.84,0:12:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰士的靈魂\N才會在滿溢的悲傷裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.97,0:13:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高尚地在閃耀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.31,0:13:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我一起落入地獄吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.15,0:13:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天真純樸的鋼彈駕駛員們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.72,0:13:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直看著你們的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.95,0:13:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心底不得不發抖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.66,0:13:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而你們把內心的某種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.49,0:13:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚至連我注定的命運也改變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.13,0:13:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪吒，我們一定要強大起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.77,0:13:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愚蠢的羅姆斐拉財國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.70,0:13:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從戰爭中奪去人性的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.11,0:13:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我或許就被迫一定要親手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.48,0:13:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把名為OZ的組織消滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.51,0:13:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，時代把命運託負給他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.78,0:13:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,年輕人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.35,0:13:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在黑暗裡看見甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.67,0:14:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不斷戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.54,0:14:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和推動時代的和平對抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.32,0:14:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯大人希望戰鬥嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.36,0:14:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥是唯一的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.30,0:14:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不戰鬥就不能誕生任何東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.44,0:14:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.17,0:14:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.94,0:14:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯‧馬吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.78,0:14:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，我永遠的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.01,0:14:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米利亞爾特‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.31,0:14:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ正在改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.32,0:14:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的力量已不足夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.79,0:14:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉…不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.02,0:14:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類要走的路太任性了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.12,0:14:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到擴張的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.49,0:15:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會把人類的心遣棄到這地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.33,0:15:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米利亞，有另一個了解我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.03,0:15:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是關懷我\N擁有兩顆心靈的女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.24,0:15:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你，替我救她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.54,0:15:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是為了實現理想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.61,0:15:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了特列斯大人而戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.56,0:15:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯，我才沒有力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.56,0:15:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為在這場混亂的戰鬥裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.93,0:15:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只能走士兵之路啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.30,0:15:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請帶我去巴爾吉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.24,0:15:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這時候，我開始發覺到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.68,0:15:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰爭不只是實現理想的手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.78,0:15:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯大人一定一直好想告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.26,0:16:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任務失敗嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.06,0:16:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到你破壞不了基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.70,0:16:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又殺不了博士他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.56,0:16:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別那樣說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.53,0:16:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…值得我來這裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.40,0:16:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高興啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.21,0:16:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你和我的正在改良啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.28,0:16:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好期待啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.05,0:16:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等著瞧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.35,0:16:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定會再次變成死神啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.95,0:16:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晚安…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.92,0:16:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使失去\N為宇宙衛星戰鬥的意義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.66,0:16:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使自己被逮住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.43,0:16:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使失去心愛的機體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.96,0:16:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那班鋼彈駕駛員們也會繼續戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.90,0:16:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾?甚麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.61,0:16:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.94,0:16:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要用這部鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.34,0:16:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把瘋狂的宇宙的一切毀滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.38,0:17:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想你告訴大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.55,0:17:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要在我面前出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.36,0:17:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說過不要接近我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.11,0:17:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,驚人的意志力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.01,0:17:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,驚人的純真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.35,0:17:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我和他們固然是敵對的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.48,0:17:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但大家尋求的戰鬥姿態\N沒有什麼不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.92,0:17:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見，希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.33,0:17:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦!快離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.93,0:17:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜葉特要爆炸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.14,0:17:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.95,0:18:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.22,0:18:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來不得不承認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.99,0:18:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是…\N這時代不再需要的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.70,0:18:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.34,0:18:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪爾麥優侯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.11,0:18:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我對羅姆斐拉財團要走的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.78,0:18:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不敢茍同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.18,0:18:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.48,0:18:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為人類須要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.38,0:18:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並非絕對的勝利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.02,0:18:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是戰鬥的姿態和理念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.35,0:18:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但使用MD般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.99,0:18:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無心的戰鬥兵器建立的時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.69,0:18:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會成為被後世不恥的文化吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.39,0:18:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.33,0:18:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在他們充滿純真的感情前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.20,0:18:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳統會看不清楚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.27,0:19:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.77,0:19:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，你是說羅姆斐拉財團總部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.24,0:19:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從你手上沒收OZ比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.44,0:19:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要把你軟禁在羅姆斐拉財團總部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.45,0:19:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我也下了決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.69,0:19:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要保佑和愛護
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.96,0:19:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能在戰場繼續閃耀的他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.59,0:19:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是不能理解的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.53,0:19:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你和我才成為敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.07,0:19:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要逃嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.54,0:19:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我先要報仇啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.32,0:19:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我心愛的蕾蒂‧安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.99,0:20:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.14,0:20:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在遙遠眾星閃耀的彼方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.67,0:20:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,追溯至很久以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.51,0:20:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從我遙遠的那心願起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.81,0:20:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時間馬上流逝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.12,0:20:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新星作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.22,0:20:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉團沒理由會容許
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.02,0:20:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仍然擁立我的士兵叛變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.26,0:20:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而他們為了\N取得地球上所有權力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.56,0:20:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把量產型MD-比爾哥降下地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.67,0:20:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我沒資格談論這次行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.25,0:21:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呢，希洛，去地球吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.68,0:21:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.35,0:21:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然拋下鋼彈離去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.95,0:21:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他有甚麼打算呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.69,0:21:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，這部機動戰士
